          "line": 90,
          "description": "<html><head></head><body><p>When given a serialize value from a JSON object this method must\nreturn the deserialized value for the record attribute.</p>\n<p>Example</p>\n<div class=\"highlight javascript\">\n      <div class=\"ribbon\"></div>\n      <div class=\"scroller\">\n        <table class=\"CodeRay\">\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td class=\"line-numbers\"><pre>1\n2\n3\n</pre></td>\n              <td class=\"code\"><pre>deserialize(serialized, options) {\n  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> empty(serialized) ? <span class=\"literal\">null</span> : <span class=\"built_in\">Number</span>(serialized)<span class=\"comment\">;</span>\n}</pre></td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n</body></html>",
